Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:57.74,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う毎日が　増えてゆくけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:07.65,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互いの気持ちはいつも　側にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:17.39,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ふたり会えなくても　平気だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:27.09,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強がり言うけど　溜め息まじりね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:37.47,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}過ぎてゆく季節に　置いてきた宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:42.29,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大切なピースの…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:57.74,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦肩而過的日子  總是在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:07.65,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}兩人的想法卻不會變  就在彼此身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:17.39,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算不能相見  也毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:27.09,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}逞強的話語裏  卻藏著嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:37.47,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}藏在逝去季節裏的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:42.29,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是缺少的一片…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服飾和小道具也要做？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是做不到就要寫別的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…這種事不用去做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓大家看到我寫的劇本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去做設計
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我…做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  美笑  那樣的話就得努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有構思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有…基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…本來也沒打算畫成圖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就先那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照構思一點點做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用著急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花點時間的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離最後綵排只剩兩星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒過來推算一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備材料和實際動手…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我也會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起做大概會花多少時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  設計的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,構思只在美笑的腦中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有美笑才能畫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的是很過分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在做什麼啊  和小孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會痛苦很正常  是那幫人太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了  真的對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油試試的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好的話可以幫我看下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次讓我聽聽意見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起劇本更能提出點好的意見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…白天的時候對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審查的時間突然提早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  打電話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽我說這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是筱塚  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎  美笑和田丸的那事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年？  我們不是還沒入學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是入學了還不得鬧個天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團的那些學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是去年開始吧  就不怎麼來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  我也沒多少和你在學校裏遇見的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為美笑一直很正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是在逞強  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在在意我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是…成熟的表現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又為什麼對那樣的美笑置之不理？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底都做了什麼  彰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都說不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…很在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是如此吧  畢竟你在和那鄰家女孩交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  比如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年和由綺見面的時候僅僅…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候她還沒有出道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把教授牽扯進來  在系裏造成了大騷動是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是第二件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在說的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四件  最後美笑還是拒絕了田丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田丸覺得那是對他的羞辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就對準備退出戲劇部的美笑說不需要退出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒讓她退出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意讓她不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她成了強制幽靈部員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼做些別人不做的雜務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪美笑會這樣想不開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟放過這次機會的話  就沒下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經沒關繫了吧  她和那個叫田丸的部長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田丸現在的女朋友是今年剛進來的部員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那樣就好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服飾和小道具都做出來的話就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真像漫畫裏的主人公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行  昨天也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說是什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多餘的話…別說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  整體過一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  …
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  腦子有點混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去你那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的預定是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在車上等您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…筱塚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒去見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  沒想到你能忍到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你獎勵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意義的  這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼要不要的  再說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看一…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事啦  只是睡眠不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡就行了吧？也沒其它的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得醒醒神才行  難得讓你給我評價
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以先睡著  我會自己看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶喝完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑咖啡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦藤井君  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害  太厲害了美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  由綺？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君  嗯…  現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全…沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在睡覺？還是有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  前不久跟彰他們玩太瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居變得很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  所以啊那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了的事啊  還有那奇怪的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在車裏偶然看到遙就趕忙寫下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得讓她看懂了不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是冬彌君也看不懂的話就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看懂了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是呢  去不了真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那只是我的任性而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天開始我就在錄新曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺非常緊張  想讓你分我一點勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  馬上就能錄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是最後的休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我給你打過一次電話的  你出去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我回了趟家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸的身體稍有不適
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親病了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是他的老病惡化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一把年紀了真拿那老頭沒辦法  雖然跟年齡無關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你沒有勉強自己過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裏出了那麼大的事  要是你還來的話  我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以說沒什麼大事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再給你電話的  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說鋼鐵五社遭受了戰後最大的赤字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候才應該把待遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藤井君  是給藤井君打電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎很忙  完全聯繫不上所以我很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒跟他約好見面或者是去哪玩  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  那麼再來一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了  說明會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說就用這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過了？很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面要怎麼辦呢  我完全沒考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  去買材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧  在電話裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？你一人不可能做到吧  只剩兩周了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:17:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道我能幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能這麼向你撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得找個幫手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫手嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙就不用問了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把彰拉來怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧  他說是今年倍受關注  要上演節目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了聽說了  是要重現著名推理小說的事件現場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰太一本正經了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說只有我們兩人而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很看好你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是看看布料  板子之類的材料就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的話不可能完成的  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話是這樣說  果然用腳來運還是有限度的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  開我家的車出來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有駕照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的技術沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬虎虎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  空白期多長了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年左右？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是用腳運吧  才不要坐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  看我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  那個餐具  用得上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃飯那個場景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  非常精簡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且感覺不到特定的時代和地點  不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是由綺？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  全都不行  完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  她已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就用剪輯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後有什麼安排？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就繼續吧  直到完成為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前線慰問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:29.14,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（夕風大學設計同好會）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這狀況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很抱歉  不過不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在角落裏就行了  能不能借用一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  可以的話借我一台縫紉機…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種好事啊  澤倉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這時期了  還想一個人插進來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是演劇部的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不可能了  到今天才突然過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各社團不都事先提出活動預定的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑  去借部室啊練習場之類的不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉江  能來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七頁  印象必須不斷加深
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它會從開端慢慢崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

